==制作==
{{Quote box|width=40%|align=right|quote=“（电影中）查理所经历的情感都是真的，反映了我试图撰写这部剧本时的真实感觉。当然有部分内容为了电影情节发展的需要做了改动或是夸张化。观看这部电影的一部分体验，是把唐纳德看成是编剧的一分子，看成电影的一部分，看成这个故事的一部分。”|source=——查理·卡夫曼对本片剧本的感想<ref name="spence-ign">{{cite news|author=Spence D|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/12/05/spike-jonze-and-charlie-kaufman-discuss-adaptation|title=Spike Jonze and Charlie Kaufman Discuss ''Adaptation''|publisher=IGN|date=2002-12-05|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218192209/http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/12/05/spike-jonze-and-charlie-kaufman-discuss-adaptation|archive-date=2015-02-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}

将苏琳·奥尔琳的《兰花窃贼》改编成电影的想法可以追溯到1994年<ref name="desowitz-variety">{{cite news|author=Bill Desowittz|url=http://variety.com/2002/scene/markets-festivals/development-players-make-personal-choices-1117871334/|title=Development players make personal choices|work=Variety|date=2002-08-18|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130718101717/http://variety.com/2002/scene/markets-festivals/development-players-make-personal-choices-1117871334/|archive-date=2013-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[20世纪福克斯公司|20世纪福克斯公司]]于1997年购买了这本书的电影改编版权<ref name="jones-variety">{{cite news |author=Oliver Jones |title=Cruise in tune with ''Shaggs'' project |url=http://variety.com/1999/film/news/cruise-in-tune-with-shaggs-project-1117760122/ |work=Variety |date=1999-12-17 |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023075015/http://variety.com/1999/film/news/cruise-in-tune-with-shaggs-project-1117760122/ |archive-date=2013-10-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，不过之后转卖给了[[強納森·德米|強納森·德米]]，后者将这个项目带到了[[哥倫比亞電影公司|哥倫比亞電影公司]]。公司于是聘请[[查理·卡夫曼|查理·卡夫曼]]来编写剧本，但卡夫曼发现这本书中缺少可用的具体情节，于是深陷脑闭塞中<ref name="bing-variety">{{cite news|author=Jonathan Bing|url=http://variety.com/2001/film/news/lit-properties-are-still-hottest-tickets-1117794235/|title=Lit properties are still hottest tickets|work=Variety|date=2001-02-26|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130718101808/http://variety.com/2001/film/news/lit-properties-are-still-hottest-tickets-1117794235/|archive-date=2013-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他之后根据自己改编过程中的经历并加以夸张创作了这个剧本，还给自己增加了一个叫唐纳德·卡夫曼的“兄弟”。查理把唐纳德的名字写上了剧本的作者名单，并且在电影的节尾用字幕提示本片是献给这个人<ref name="brodesser-variety-1110">{{cite news|author=Claude Brodesser|url=http://variety.com/1999/film/news/scribe-revisiting-reality-1117757917/|title=Scribe revisiting reality|work=Variety|date=1999-11-10|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023075039/http://variety.com/1999/film/news/scribe-revisiting-reality-1117757917/|archive-date=2013-10-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1999年9月，卡夫曼已经完成了两稿剧本<ref name="kaufman-second-draft">{{cite news |author=Charlie Kaufman |url=http://www.beingcharliekaufman.com/adaptation.pdf |title=''Adaptation.'': Second Draft |publisher=BeingCharlieKaufman.com |date=1999-09-24 |accessdate=2008-04-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080407235615/http://www.beingcharliekaufman.com/adaptation.pdf |archivedate=2008-04-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，2000年11月又开始撰写第三稿<ref name="kaufman-nov2000-draft">{{cite news |author=Charlie Kaufman |url=http://www.beingcharliekaufman.com/adaptationnov2000.pdf |title=''Adaptation.'': Revised Draft |publisher=BeingCharlieKaufman.com |date=2000-11-21 |accessdate=2008-04-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080407235612/http://www.beingcharliekaufman.com/adaptationnov2000.pdf |archivedate=2008-04-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

卡夫曼表示：<blockquote>“我很晚才想到应该怎么创作这部电影（的剧本）。我当时也只能想到这么一个主意，不过我对之很满意，而且我知道，要是自己把这个主意透露出去，肯定没有人会赞同，所以我就只是低头写啊写，一直没告诉任何人。只有在拍摄《[[成为约翰·马尔科维奇|约翰·马尔科维奇]]》期间我有向斯派克·琼斯透露，他也知道我那段时间有多失意，而他都说，我已经疯了，所以我也不知道这剧本写出来会成个什么样儿。”<ref name="fleming-variety-1114">{{cite news |author=Michael Fleming |url=http://variety.com/2002/film/news/what-will-follow-film-success-for-eminem-1117876083/ |title=What will follow film success for Eminem? |work=Variety |date=2002-11-14 |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130718101942/http://variety.com/2002/film/news/what-will-follow-film-success-for-eminem-1117876083/ |archive-date=2013-07-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref></blockquote>此外他还表示：“我（当时）真觉得自己的做法是在拿事业开玩笑！”<ref name="stax-ign-0313">{{cite news|author=Stax|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/03/13/charlie-kaufman-talks-shop|title=Charles Kaufman Talks Shop|publisher=IGN|date=2002-03-13|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020153328/http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/03/13/charlie-kaufman-talks-shop|archive-date=2013-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2000年4月，《改编剧本》进入了制作的快速轨道，卡夫曼在这一期间仍然进行了一些改动<ref name="fleming-variety-0406">{{cite news |author=Michael Fleming |title=Brothers in a Conundrum; Rat Pack lives |work=Variety |url=http://variety.com/2000/voices/columns/brothers-in-a-conundrum-rat-pack-lives-1117780287/ |date=2000-04-06 |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023075033/http://variety.com/2000/voices/columns/brothers-in-a-conundrum-rat-pack-lives-1117780287/ |archive-date=2013-10-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2000年6月，[[IGN|IGN]]网站的斯科特·布拉克从[[互联网|互联网]]把剧本泄露了出去<ref name="brake-ign">{{cite news |author=Scott Brake |title=Script Review of Charlie Kaufman's ''Adaptation'' |publisher=IGN |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/08/script-review-of-charlie-kaufmans-adaptation |date=2000-06-08 |accessdate=2013-07-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020153330/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/08/script-review-of-charlie-kaufmans-adaptation |archivedate=2013-10-20 }}</ref>，到了10月，[[Ain't_It_Cool_News|Ain't It Cool News]]网站的{{link-en|德鲁·麦克文尼|Drew McWeeny}}也予以跟进<ref name="moriarty-aicn">{{cite news|author=Drew "Moriarty" McWeeny|url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/7162|title=Moriarty Rumbles About ''Adaptation'', ''The Royal Tenenbaums'', and ''Catch Me If You Can''!|publisher=Ain't It Cool News|date=2000-10-10|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020112614/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/7162|archive-date=2013-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。跨媒体制片公司加入这个项目，并以对电影投资来换取国际市场发行权，哥伦比亚公司于是只负责北美市场<ref name="lyons-variety">{{cite news|author=Charles Lyons|url=http://variety.com/2001/film/news/helmers-let-out-a-rebel-yell-1117801603/|title=Helmers let out a rebel yell|work=Variety|date=2001-06-18|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023082925/http://variety.com/2001/film/news/helmers-let-out-a-rebel-yell-1117801603/|archive-date=2013-10-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影的拍摄工作于2001年3月末在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]开始并于6月结束<ref name="Schmitz" />。

==反响==
哥伦比亚电影公司曾宣布于2001年末发行《改编剧本》<ref name="Schmitz" />，但影片一直到2002年12月6日才开始在美国进行限量发行，2003年2月14日起才在全国范围上映，首周一共在672家电影院收入113万零480美元。最终在北美的票房为2250万美元，其他国家1030万美元，合计3280万美元<ref name="box-office-mojo">{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=adaptation.htm|title=Adaptation. (2002)|publisher=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65U6Pv5XB?url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=adaptation.htm|archive-date=2012-02-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影获得了良好的评价，根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的197篇专业评论文章，其中179篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为91%，平均评分8.2（最高10分）<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1118700-adaptation/ |title=Adaptation (2002) |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130621074148/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1118700-adaptation/ |archive-date=2013-06-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的40篇评论文章中有36篇给出好评，2篇差评，2篇褒贬不一，得分83（满分100）<ref name="metacritic">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/adaptation|title=Adaptation. (2002): Reviews|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730213240/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/adaptation|archive-date=2013-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》影评专栏作家[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]称赞本片“让你好奇得有些呼吸困难”，“观看这部电影的过程将让人体验到创作过程中的挑战”<ref name="ebert-initialreview">{{cite news |author=Roger Ebert |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/adaptation-2002 |title=Adaptation |work=Chicago Sun-Times |date=2002-12-20 |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607172318/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/adaptation-2002 |archivedate=2013-06-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，他于2008年将《改编剧本》列入自己选择的“伟大电影”收藏名单中，2009年末，他把这部电影评为10年来最优秀的作品之一<ref name="ebert-greatmovies">{{cite web |author=Roger Ebert |title=Adaptation |date=2008-09-18 |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/great-movie-adaptation-2002 |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602122841/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/great-movie-adaptation-2002 |archivedate=2013-06-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》的韦斯利·莫里斯（{{lang|en|Wesley Morris}}）认为“这是一部史诗般风趣、悲惨、严苛、古怪、原创、大胆和真诚的电影”<ref name="morris-boston">{{cite news |author=Wesley Morris |url=http://www.boston.com/movies/display?display=movie&id=1810 |title=A revolutionary look at the evolution of creativity |work=The Boston Globe |date=2002-12-20 |accessdate=2011-08-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810065358/http://www.boston.com/movies/display?display=movie&id=1810 |archivedate=2011-08-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》的大卫·安森（{{lang|en|David Ansen}}）感觉梅丽尔·斯特里普“已经好多年没有出演过这么有意思的角色了”<ref name="ansen-newsweek">{{cite news |author=David Ansen |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/newsweek/2002/12/08/meta-movie-madness.html |title=Meta-Movie Madness |work=Newsweek |date=2002-12-09 |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120919233657/http://www.thedailybeast.com/newsweek/2002/12/08/meta-movie-madness.html |archivedate=2012-09-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。不过，《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》的麦克·克拉克（{{lang|en|Mike Clark}}）对电影给出了较为负面的评价，主要批评了结尾有些过于得意忘形，污辱了观众的智商，“就像给自己脚上打了一枪般扇了目标观众的耳光”<ref name="clark-usatoday">{{cite news |author=Mike Clark |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2002-12-05-adaptation_x.htm |title=Cage's ''Adaptation''? Sorry, Charlie |work=USA Today |date=2002-12-05 |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020052444/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2002-12-05-adaptation_x.htm |archivedate=2012-10-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

在[[第75届奥斯卡金像奖|第75届奥斯卡金像奖]]角逐中，《改编剧本》获得了[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|男主角]]（尼古拉斯·凯奇）、[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|男配角]]（克里斯·库柏）、[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|女配角]]（梅丽尔·斯特里普）、[[奥斯卡最佳原著改编奖|原著改编]]（查理·卡夫曼和唐纳德·卡夫曼）4项提名，其中克里斯·库柏成功胜出，唐纳德也成为历史上首位获[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]提名的虚构“真人”<ref name="Oscars2003">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/75th-winners.html |title=The 75th Academy Awards (2003) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2011-11-20 |work=oscars.org |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224032945/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/75th-winners.html |archive-date=2013-12-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2003/2003-02-12-oscar-race_x.htm |title=In Many categories a two way race |publisher=USA Today |accessdate=2013-07-18 |date=2003-02-12 |author1=Scott Bowles |author2=Claudia Puig |author3=Andy Seiler |author4=Susan Wloszczyna |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103181617/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2003/2003-02-12-oscar-race_x.htm |archive-date=2012-11-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Could Donald Kaufman get an Oscar trophy |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,427367,00.html |accessdate=2013-07-18 |date=2003-02-28 |publisher=EW.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722215144/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,427367,00.html |archive-date=2013-07-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而在第60届金球奖角逐中，本片也获得了[[金球奖最佳音乐及喜剧电影|最佳影片（音乐剧/喜剧类）]]、[[金球奖最佳导演|导演]]（斯派克·琼斯）、[[金球奖最佳音乐及喜剧类电影男主角|电影男主角（音乐剧/喜剧类）]]、[[金球奖最佳电影男配角|电影男配角]]、[[金球奖最佳电影女配角|电影女配角]]和[[金球奖最佳剧本|编剧]]6项提名，最终库柏和斯特里普分别拿下了最佳电影男、女配角奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,401271,00.html |title=Global Warming |publisher=EW.com |author=Brian Hiatt |date=2002-12-19 |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522171540/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,401271,00.html |archive-date=2013-05-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,625341,00.html |author=Stephen M. Silverman |date=2002-12-19 |accessdate=2013-07-18 |title='Chicago' Strikes Gold with the Globes |publisher=People.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130304091953/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,625341,00.html |archive-date=2013-03-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="imdb-2003-goldenglobes">{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000292/2003 |title=Golden Globes, USA 2003 |date=2003-01-19 |publisher=Internet Movie Database |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080423213308/http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Golden_Globes_USA/2003 |archivedate=2008-04-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。卡夫曼还获得了第56届[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]最佳改编剧-{}-本奖，凯奇、库柏和斯特里普分别获得了提名<ref name="imdb-2003-bafta">{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/BAFTA_Awards/2003 |title=BAFTA Awards: 2003 |publisher=Internet Movie Database |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080423213309/http://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/BAFTA_Awards/2003 |archivedate=2008-04-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。此外，《改编剧本》还是[[美国影艺协会|美国影艺协会]]评选的年度电影之一，获2003年[[柏林国际电影节|柏林国际电影节]]评审团大奖，[[波士顿影评人协会|波士顿影评人协会]]、[[广播影评人协会|广播影评人协会]]、[[芝加哥影评人协会|芝加哥影评人协会]]、[[纽约影评人协会|纽约影评人协会]]等多个影评人协会的最佳编剧奖<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0268126/awards |title=Awards for Adaptation. (2002) |publisher=IMDb |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130328193536/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0268126/awards |archive-date=2013-03-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

